---
import LearnBtn from "../../unitComponents/LearnBtn.astro";
import Whatsbtn from "../../unitComponents/Whatsbtn.astro";
import Logo from "../../../assets/logos/LogoTriasoMX.svg";
import Cabins from "../../../assets/images/Service/Spare/SpareCabine.jpg";
---

<section class="w-full font-bold text-grisT mt-28">
    <div class="w-full px-8 md:px-52">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl text-end">
            MAINTENANCE
        </h1>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div class="w-full px-8 md:px-52">
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
            Triaso’s maintenance services are designed to keep your equipment operating at peak performance, minimizing downtime and maximizing efficiency.
            <br>Our team of expert technicians, operators, and engineers meticulously inspects, services, and optimizes every component of your asphalt plant.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full bg-[url(/Gallery/drum-mixer.jpg)] bg-cover bg-center h-[70vh] mt-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 px-8 md:px-52 gap-16 justify-center items-center w-full h-full bg-white/70">
            <div class="w-full col-span-1">
            <Whatsbtn></Whatsbtn>
            </div>
            <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2 w-full text-end">
                <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-black">24/7 CUSTOMER SERVICE</h1>
                <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl">
                    OUR TEAM IS AVAILABLE AROUND THE CLOCK, READY TO ASSIST YOU AT ANY TIME, EVEN ON WEEKENDS AND HOLIDAYS.
                </h2>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full px-8 md:px-52 bg-blueMain py-16 text-white">
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
            Comprehensive phone support for maintenance and fault diagnosis is available to all equipment owners—both original
             and subsequent—throughout the product’s entire lifespan. Our experts are ready to guide you through solutions and
              help ensure your asphalt plant operates at peak efficiency for years to come.
        </p><br>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
            Additionally, we have a team of skilled technicians ready to provide prompt on-site assistance for future relocations
             or servicing, guaranteeing uninterrupted equipment performance.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full bg-[url(/Gallery/drum-mixer.jpg)] bg-cover bg-center h-[70vh]">
        <div class="w-full h-full bg-white/70 px-8 md:px-72 py-16 text-black">
            <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl">USER MANUAL</h1><br>
            <p class="text-base md:text-lg">
                We provide the most complete user manual in the industry for equipment installation and maintenance.
                This allows you to independently
                handle future installations and perform full maintenance with confidence.
            </p>
            <div>
                <img src="" alt="">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full px-8 md:px-52 py-16">
        <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-blueMain text-center">Technical and Professional Focus</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 pl-8 md:pl-52 items-center">
        <div class="w-full col-span-1">
            <img src={Cabins.src} alt="" class="rounded-2xl">
        </div>
        <div class="w-full col-span-1">
            <div class="w-full rounded-l-2xl bg-redBg p-8">
                <h2 class="text-white text-lg md:text-xl">
                    Available anytime for immediate equipment support
                </h2>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 justify-center items-center px-8 md:px-52">
        <div class="w-full py-10">
            <h2 class="font-bold text-blueMain text-lg md:text-xl">
                Tailored upgrades
            </h2><br>
            <p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg">
                We evaluate your current setup and suggest only the upgrades
                 that will truly improve your plant’s performance, safety, and compliance.
            </p><br>
            <h2 class="font-bold text-grisT text-lg md:text-xl">
                Compatibility guaranteed
            </h2><br>
            <p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg">
                We adapt our solutions to fit your existing systems, regardless of the original
                 brand or age of the equipment.
            </p><br>
            <h2 class="font-bold text-redBg text-lg md:text-xl">
                Structural and mechanical reinforcements
            </h2><br>
            <p class="font-thin text-base md:text-lg">
                We rebuild worn-out parts, reinforce critical components, and install updated systems
                 to extend your equipment’s lifespan.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <img src="" alt="">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div>
        <img src="" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="w-full bg-grisT relative h-[250px]">
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-10 w-full">
            <img src={Logo.src} alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="w-full h-full px-8 md:px-52 text-white text-base md:text-lg relative z-20 justify-center flex flex-col">
            <p>
            With a proactive approach to maintenance, we work to extend the lifespan of
             your equipment and ensure consistent reliability.
            </p><br>
            <p>
                Backed by rigorous quality control and advanced engineering techniques, our
                systems are built for seamless, long-term operation—giving you the confidence
                to focus on your projects without unexpected interruptions
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full text-center my-16">
        <h1 class="font-bold text-blueMain text-2xl md:text-3xl">
            Triaso® Spare Parts
        </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full px-8 md:px-64 mb-16">
        <div class="w-full bg-[url(/Gallery/Boxes.jpg)] bg-cover bg-center h-[70vh] rounded-lg">
            <div class="w-full h-full bg-black/70 text-white text-base md:text-lg flex flex-col justify-center px-16">
                <p>No other asphalt plant manufacturer in the world produces as many of its own components as Triaso.</p><br>
                <p>
                    This vertical integration allows us to offer unmatched service, warranty coverage, and direct support—both
                    from our factory in Mexico and our distributor in the United States.    
                </p><br>
                <p>
                    We ship spare parts worldwide to ensure your production never stops. Every part is backed by guaranteed quality,
                    competitive pricing, and fast delivery times.
                </p>
                <div class="mt-16 flex justify-center">
                    <LearnBtn></LearnBtn>
                </div>
                </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>